after installation of java , copy the path and go to environments variables
choose path and add C:\Program Files\Java\jdk-18.0.2.1\bin
after new  variable name = JAVA_HOME value=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk-18.0.2.1
chect java -version , javac -version to see if installation was good

from broswer find apache maven 
download .zib extract copy the directory apache-maven-3.8.6 and paste in c:/progam files
GO to environment variables
edit path and new C:\Program Files\apache-maven-3.8.6\bin
name=MAVEN_HOME value= C:\Program Files\apache-maven-3.8.6
name=M2_HOME value=C:\Program Files\apache-maven-3.8.6

create a maven program from scratch
cmd create dev directory goto c:/>dev
mvn archytype:generate
